                <h1>Understanding SOC 2 Background Check Requirements</h1>
                <p>When conducting SOC 2 background checks, businesses must verify employees' criminal records, employment history, and education credentials. These checks ensure that staff members meet the integrity and trustworthiness standards essential for data security and privacy. Compliance with SOC 2 helps establish credibility and safeguard customer data.</p>
